name: Pop Rocks Child Scarf
description:
Pop rocks is a child size scarf, Full of color and brightness, bringing a smile to any child's face. 

ﻬ Made from Baby yarn, extremely soft.
ﻬTightly woven with single strand knit stitch. Keeps you super warm!

name: Pastel egg Scarf
description:
An extemely soft adult scarf. Made in Baby Yarn. It is multi-colored, single strand yarn knitted and designed with a wide angled end on both sides.  Super bright and colorful, this is perfect for any sweet tooth, reminds me of sweet tarts! 

All pieces are handmade with care. Created in a house free of pet hair and smoke.
